python-fll (0.9.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Add fll shell wrapper and python program which uses the fll modules.
  * Add cmdline.py, main.py and config.py fll module skeletons.
  * Switch to argparse module for option/argument parsing.
  * Remove Makefile, leave build system to setup.py.
  * Remove defunct test suite.
  * Build manual page for fll build tool dynamically based on argparse
    formatted help/usage output.
  * Clean up manual page with distutls clean subcommand.
  * Remove fll_detect_locale_pkgs and manpage, they are not used and
    fll.locales is pending overhaul.
  * Install a ConfigObj spec file for configuration validation.
  * Remove x bit from fll/locales.py.
  * Do configuration file validation, set default values in validation
    specification.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Wed, 29 Dec 2010 22:45:46 +1000

